snippet.title: Australia The Law Is The Law Johnny Depp Amber Heard
snippet.description:
08.05.2020 

I was wondering what other countries can do with information that were revealed during the libel law suit. I came across an article (link below) that discussed the Australia's incident with Amber Heard's dogs.

Article link:
'They're not above the law': MP Barnaby Joyce says Johnny Depp's ex-wife Amber Heard could face perjury charges on return to Australia
https://amp.nine.com.au/article/d5bf4fc8-8c77-4fd4-873e-2463c59f2126

Lost Beyond Pluto (YouTuber with legal knowledge)
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOp24og-YLLuvUP4yrJ2cJA
